Paper: hep-th/9504039

Date: 1995-04-07

Title: Trace anomaly in the field-antifield formalism

Authors: J. Barcelos-Neto, N.R.F. Braga and S.M. de Souza

Comments: 7 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: Class.Quant.Grav. 13 (1996) 1149-1154

The field-antifield quantization method is used to calculate the traceanomaly for a massless scalar field in a curved background, by means of thezeta function regularization procedure.